item.description:
&lt;h1 id=&#34;checkout-cancelled&#34;&gt;Checkout Cancelled&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No charge was made. Your products are still available if you&amp;rsquo;d like to complete your purchase.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;continue-shopping&#34;&gt;Continue Shopping&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;/store/&#34;&gt;View all products&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Or return to the product page you were viewing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;questions&#34;&gt;Questions?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you had trouble with checkout, &lt;a href=&#34;mailto:support@edgelesslab.com&#34;&gt;let us know&lt;/a&gt; and we&amp;rsquo;ll help you out.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Still interested? Come back anytime — products include lifetime updates.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h1 id=&#34;thank-you-&#34;&gt;Thank You! 🎉&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your payment was successful. You should receive an email shortly with your download link.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;whats-next&#34;&gt;What&amp;rsquo;s Next?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Check your email&lt;/strong&gt; — Look for a message from Edgeless Lab with your download link&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Download your product&lt;/strong&gt; — Click the secure link in the email&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Start building&lt;/strong&gt; — Follow the included guide to get started&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;need-help&#34;&gt;Need Help?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Can&amp;rsquo;t find the email?&lt;/strong&gt; Check your spam folder or &lt;a href=&#34;mailto:support@edgelesslab.com&#34;&gt;contact support&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Download link expired?&lt;/strong&gt; Links are valid for 7 days — contact us for a refresh&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Questions about the product?&lt;/strong&gt; Reply to the confirmation email&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Thanks for supporting Edgeless Lab. We&amp;rsquo;d love to hear what you build!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
